Class EventStorageJdbcImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.AbstractEventStorageJdbcImpl
        • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.EventStorageJdbcImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractEventStorageJdbc, ApplicationConfiguration, ApplicationModule, EventStorage, EventStorageJdbc

    public class EventStorageJdbcImpl
extends AbstractEventStorageJdbcImpl
implements EventStorageJdbc
    An implementation of the model object 'Event Storage Jdbc'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Jdbc Driver Name
    • Driver Bundles
    • Max Field Length
    • Query Fetch Size
